 <message filing_url="http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/74303/000007430325000071/oln-20250331.htm" severity="error" effectiveDate="2024-08-31" cid="2845526208784">[DQC.US.0179.10143] The filing has used the DividendsAxis with the member us-gaap:MeasurementInputExpectedDividendRateMember, but has used the concept us-gaap:CommonStockDividendsPerShareDeclared multiple times on this axis with different period contexts. The concept us-gaap:CommonStockDividendsPerShareDeclared has been used mutiple times to capture the values 0.2 and 0.2 for the periods 2025-01-01 to 2025-03-31 and 2024-01-01 to 2024-03-31.  The DividendAxis should use discrete members to represent different dividend events. The same concept should not be used more than once with the same dividend member us-gaap:MeasurementInputExpectedDividendRateMember.

